{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Toolbar entries must have sequential item_0, item_1...; otherwise REAPER ignores following items.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab ActionCommandID-strings must begin with "_" (e.g. "_RS...").\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab If a referenced script file does not exist, it will be skipped (but MenuSet will still be non-empty if any exist).\sa180\par}
