{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Features:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab MODE=BEAT:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li720 \fi-360 \endash \tx360\tab Sucht Kicks, Snares, HiHats in der DB.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li720 \fi-360 \endash \tx360\tab Nutzt AI-Labels (z.B. "Drum", "Kick drum", "Snare", "Hi-hat") und/oder Dateinamen (kick/snare/hat) + UCS Category (DRUMS).\par}
