{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel0 \b \fs36 DF95 Toolbar Suite (Generated Repo)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 This repository snapshot was generated from the {\f1 df95-ifls-full} repo and is focused on {\b toolbars + all scripts/resources they require}.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel1 \b \fs32 Quick workflow\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 1.\tx360\tab Install via ReaPack using {\f1 index.xml} (after you host this repo on GitHub).\par}
